text: James Rand McNally (born January 30, 1944) is an American politician. He is the 50th and current Lieutenant Governor of Tennessee since 2017. He is a member of the Republican Party. He was a member of the Tennessee Senate since 1987. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Lieutenant Governors of Tennessee Category:Politicians from Massachusetts Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
